Due to the Assembly Station Project, alternate shuttle buses will replace Orange Line trains in both directions from Sullivan to Oak Grove Stations from start to end of service during the following weekends: 

- Saturday, May 2, 2015, through Sunday, May 3, 2015.
- Saturday, May 16, 2015, through Sunday, May 17, 2015.
- Saturday, May 30, 2015, through Sunday, May 31, 2015.

Regular Orange Line trains will resume at the start of service on Mondays. All shuttle bus stops are accessible for persons with disabilities. 

Shuttling the following stops: 
Oak Grove Station 
Malden Center Station 
Wellington Station 
Assembly Station
Sullivan Station
alerts.header_text: Buses replacing Orange Line service between Sullivan and Oak Grove Stations on May 2-3, May 16-17, and May 30-31 from start to the end of service.
